title: Italy 15 Year Bond Yield
description: Italy 15 Year Bond was 4.27 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Italy 15 Year Bond Yield reached an all time high of 8.02 in November of 2011. This page includes a chart with historical data for Italy 15 Year Bond Yield.
author: Dipartimento del Tesoro
